{
  "stem": "1684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They said, since your sons are not here-- to me-- to my mother and to me, I have to take your husband.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he took-- they took him to the police station.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was there for eight days, and I found-- I found where he was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was standing there every day, and I was talking to the police guys.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Finally, they released him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we had to leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They had to leave anyhow, and I had to leave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I didn't know where to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were standing in line for days and days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was like [INAUDIBLE] the highest, the Jewish [NON-ENGLISH], it was called.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we were standing there, and we wanted to get some visas or so.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Only one [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one country let people go in [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Siam. ?] And I had a visa who wanted to go to-- to [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Siam. ?] But if I didn't have any choice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- in the meantime, I got a permit to go to England, to go into a hospital to learn to be a nurse or to [? kindergartner. ?] And in the meantime, my parents went to Poland, because they had to go to Poland.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I joined them instead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because my brothers-- the two brothers got their certificate to go to America, my two oldest brothers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my brother Willie had to go in 1936.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He left already for Palestine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time, it was on a British mandate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he left for Israel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my sister was taken anyhow from-- you know, from the [INAUDIBLE] to Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then she got her certificate, and she went to Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was left with my parents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went to town of where my parents are from.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
